## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **risankizumab Skyrizi 2022 Crohn + 2024 UC** = first IL-23 p19 selective FDA IBD. p19 selective (vs p40 shared) 가 IL-12 보존 + 안전성 향상 + 효능 비열등. quantum-VQE 의 IL-23 p19 pocket 직접 fit.
2. **mirikizumab Omvoh 2023 UC** = Lilly IL-23 p19 selective UC first 적응증. risankizumab/guselkumab 와 class effect + 분자별 selectivity 미세 차이.
3. **upadacitinib Rinvoq 2022 UC + 2023 Crohn** = JAK1 selective oral. tofacitinib JAK1/3 보다 selectivity 향상. quantum-VQE 의 JAK1 ATP pocket leverage.
4. **etrasimod Velsipity 2023** = S1P1/4/5 selective oral UC. ozanimod (S1P1/5) 보다 4 추가. lymphocyte 림프 trafficking 차단 + cardiac arrhythmia signal 약화.
5. **vedolizumab Entyvio 2014** = first gut-selective integrin α4β7. natalizumab (α4) PML 위험 회피 + gut-restricted. 양자-VQE 의 integrin geometry fit.
6. **ustekinumab Stelara Crohn 2016 + UC 2019** = first IL-12/23 p40. 건선 (cross-dermatology) 동일 약물 + IBD 적응증 확장.
7. **infliximab Remicade 1998** = first FDA TNF-α IBD (Crohn 1998 + UC 2005). 25+ years legacy + bio similar 다수. ADA (anti-drug antibody) + LOR (loss of response) issue.
8. **TPMT pharmacogenomics + azathioprine/6-MP** = TPMT poor metabolizer 골수 억제 위험 ↑. cross-pharmacogenomics 의 IBD 임상 가장 빈번 PGx 적용.
9. **IBD + colon cancer 위험** = 8-10년 후 colorectal cancer 위험 ↑ (UC > Crohn). 만성 염증 + dysplasia surveillance colonoscopy. cross-cancer 만성 염증 link.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, IBD specific 임상 의미 한정.

